data1.title: Mess Management Mobile App
data1.description: A cutting-edge mess management application built with Flutter and Supabase. This powerful app allows users to conveniently mark their food requirements at specific times, while wardens and mess managers can effortlessly track the daily food count through the app. By implementing messLab, the efficiency of mess management in staff hostels has significantly improved.

data1.title: Movie Recommendation System
data1.description: Movie Recommander system that recommends movie based on the content of the movie using the similarity. The model is built using the dataset from kaggle.

data1.title: Car Price Prediction
data1.description: Using the dataset available from kaggle made a used car price prediction model that can predict the price of used cars using the features given. The model is of the accuracy of 89%

data1.title: Slash_key 2.O Offical Website
data1.description: Slash_key is a 30 hour hackathon organised by IEEE CS KS. Official website for the hackathon was designed using HTML, CSS, JS and other frontend libraries such as bootstrap and was deployed. This website helped to gain reach and publicity for the hackathon thereby increased the participation
